snippet.title: Brigador Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Brigador is an upcoming tactical vehicle action game, available on Steam Early Access on October 16th, 2015. PREORDER NOW! at http://www.stellarjockeys.com 

Follow @HughSJ and @gausswerks on Twitter. 

For more screenshots and gifs check out this album on imgur: http://imgur.com/topic/Design_&_Art/ViBV2
Also check out http://www.twitch.tv/stellarjockeys and http://www.twitch.tv/gausswerks for development live streaming.
